        <updateDate>2009-08-05T14:38:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Liability for Aiding and Abetting Securities Violations Act of 2009 - Amends the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 to subject to liability in a private civil action any person that knowingly or recklessly provides substantial assistance to another person (aids and abets) in violation of such Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
